{
  "stem": "14168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there I found the Revisionist Movement, led by an inspired and inspiring man, Ze'ev Jabotinsky, who wanted to recreate and a-- and the Zionist ideal of a Jewish majority.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he ?] said, we have to be prepared, because the Arabs are not going to let us do that peacefully.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I became part of the movement of the Betar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as a result of my Jewish education, since I was, even as a student, well known at the time, I became its leader.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That we learned Hebrew-- studied Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had-- that was the first thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then Hebrew literature, also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We engaged in paramilitary exercises-- practices at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And figured that the new generation of Jews would have to add something to being a-- scholars in Talmud and being intellectuals only, that they would have to fight.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I intended to go to Israel at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was unfortunately thwarted, because Israel was-- Palestine-- hermetically closed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I-- so I went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had, in 1900-- in 1900-- in 1935, I took my high school leaving examination back to my school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My school education had not been completed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And under-- so I went to school two years under the Nazi regime.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I must say that it was very, very sad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was a tremendous shock, because overnight, some of the schoolmates that I went with didn't know us anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They took-- they dressed in Nazi uniforms, and they didn't want to have anything to do with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And some of the professors sort of played the same game.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Other professors, however-- and I know quite a few-- had a lot of guts and courage and said they didn't agree with everything that Hitler did.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
